## Key Validation & Error Patterns Summary

| Element | Pattern | Classes |
|---------|---------|---------|
| **Error border** | Add red border on error | `border-destructive` |
| **Error text** | Error message below field | `text-destructive` |
| **Helper text** | Information text below field | `text-muted-foreground`, `text-[13px]` |
| **Required indicator** | Red asterisk on label | `text-destructive` |
| **Label on error** | Label text turns red | `text-destructive` (FormLabel only) |
| **Error message size** | Smaller, semantic text | `text-xs` or `text-sm` `font-medium` |
| **Spacing** | Between label/input/error | `space-y-1` or `space-y-2` |

All validation errors use the **`text-destructive`** color token (#CE4836 - Easy Salon Red).
